Package model

Class Album

java.lang.Object
model.Album
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Album extends Object implements Serializable
This class models an album, it has a name, list of photos, the earliest photo, and the oldest photo in the album. This class implements the serializable interface.
